data.description: This is a stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home. Some key features include NO HOA, allowing you the freedom to personalize and enjoy your property without any restrictions. This home is carpet-free, making maintenance and cleaning a breeze. It also boasts a Primary Owner's Suite with Dual Vanities, as well as an Open Floor Plan - providing modern and spacious living areas that are perfect for gatherings. Enjoy nature from the comfort of your screened patio - A serene oasis to relax and unwind. This house also includes multiple smart home features, a security system, a water softener, and a reverse osmosis system for you to enjoy the benefits of clean and pure water. ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE at 3.125% - A rare opportunity to secure favorable financing terms. This beauty is located less than 2 miles from the vibrant center of Historic Downtown Sanford. Here, you will find a plethora of charming restaurants, boutique shops, a scenic marina, art galleries, and many other attractions. A 5-mile drive to Sanford International Airport for your next adventure. This is more than just a house; it's a home where cherished memories are waiting to be made. Don't miss your chance to make this beauty yours. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the perfect blend of modern comfort and the charm of Sanford.
